@startuml A008-sequence
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

actor "系統管理員" as Admin
participant "前端" as Frontend
participant "後端 API" as API
database "資料庫" as DB

== 查詢報表收件信箱清單 ==
Admin -> Frontend : 進入系統設定頁面
Frontend -> API : GET /api/settings/report-emails
API -> DB : SELECT report_recipient_emails
DB --> API : 回傳清單
API --> Frontend : 200 回傳清單
Frontend --> Admin : 顯示收件信箱清單

== 新增報表收件信箱 ==
Admin -> Frontend : 輸入 Email 並送出
Frontend -> API : POST /api/settings/report-emails
API -> API : 驗證 Email 格式
alt 格式錯誤
    API --> Frontend : 400 Email 格式錯誤
    Frontend --> Admin : 顯示格式錯誤訊息
else 格式正確
    API -> DB : INSERT report_recipient_emails
    DB --> API : 新增成功
    API --> Frontend : 201 新增成功
    Frontend --> Admin : 顯示新增成功
end

== 刪除報表收件信箱 ==
Admin -> Frontend : 選擇欲刪除的 Email
Frontend -> API : DELETE /api/settings/report-emails/{id}
API -> DB : DELETE report_recipient_emails WHERE id = {id}
DB --> API : 刪除成功
API --> Frontend : 200 刪除成功
Frontend --> Admin : 顯示刪除成功
@enduml
